00:23:21,240 --> 00:23:21,680
Serves you right.

574
00:23:23,680 --> 00:23:25,039
I mean, with our relationship...

575
00:23:25,279 --> 00:23:26,160
If you wanted to see my phone...

576
00:23:26,160 --> 00:23:27,079
You just send me a message.

577
00:23:27,079 --> 00:23:28,880
I'd zip over and deliver it to your house.

578
00:23:28,880 --> 00:23:30,200
Why bother making the trip yourself?

579
00:23:30,640 --> 00:23:32,359
You coming to my house is inviting a wolf into the den.

580
00:23:33,279 --> 00:23:34,000
Why are you insulting me?

581
00:23:34,960 --> 00:23:35,759
I'm a puppy dog.

582
00:23:35,799 --> 00:23:36,319
Okay, okay, okay.

583
00:23:36,680 --> 00:23:38,240
You know, the effort you spend guarding against me...

584
00:23:38,240 --> 00:23:39,799
You should take a good look at your Xu Rui.

585
00:23:40,079 --> 00:23:41,440
What? Now you know to be worried?

586
00:23:41,559 --> 00:23:42,119
Shut up.

587
00:23:43,759 --> 00:23:45,279
This guy looks pretty tall.

588
00:23:45,599 --> 00:23:46,240
Where's he from?

589
00:23:47,279 --> 00:23:47,759
From another school.

590
00:23:49,799 --> 00:23:50,480
Is he handsome or am I?

591
00:23:50,960 --> 00:23:51,720
Then tell me first.

592
00:23:51,880 --> 00:23:52,839
Does Cousin like puppy dogs?

593
00:23:53,200 --> 00:23:53,960
Anyway, she doesn't like you.

594
00:23:54,200 --> 00:23:54,599
He's handsome.

595
00:23:58,759 --> 00:23:59,400
Xiaocan.

596
00:24:00,000 --> 00:24:00,559
Xiaocan.

597
00:24:00,960 --> 00:24:01,359
Look.

598
00:24:02,000 --> 00:24:03,559
I received the admission letter.

599
00:24:09,200 --> 00:24:09,960
Feel better now?

600
00:24:11,000 --> 00:24:11,599
Don't move.

601
00:24:12,039 --> 00:24:13,119
This... this looks really good.

602
00:24:13,200 --> 00:24:13,839
Brother Xiaocan.

603
00:24:14,839 --> 00:24:16,119
I was also admitted to Duxing University.

604
00:24:16,400 --> 00:24:17,559
I'm in the Hydraulic Engineering major.

605
00:24:19,720 --> 00:24:20,359
That's amazing.

606
00:24:21,920 --> 00:24:23,160
Both of you don't move. Don't move.

607
00:24:47,160 --> 00:24:49,240
You've worked hard this year.

608
00:24:51,519 --> 00:24:53,640
The wish of so many years has finally come true.

609
00:24:56,039 --> 00:24:57,000
Study hard.

610
00:24:57,400 --> 00:24:58,400
Student Kong Guifang.

611
00:25:04,000 --> 00:25:04,440
Go for it.

612
00:25:34,839 --> 00:25:36,279
Everyone, stop what you're doing.

613
00:25:37,160 --> 00:25:38,480
We're closing the shop tonight.

614
00:25:38,839 --> 00:25:40,200
Take a break. Wages as usual.

615
00:25:43,559 --> 00:25:45,000
This endless rain...

616
00:25:45,000 --> 00:25:46,799
inevitably makes one feel gloomy too.

617
00:25:46,799 --> 00:25:48,279
And if you want to boost your happiness,

618
00:25:48,319 --> 00:25:50,480
what you need most right now is the company of family.

619
00:25:54,000 --> 00:25:55,039
You all have families, right?

620
00:25:56,079 --> 00:25:57,079
Go on, go home.

621
00:25:57,880 --> 00:25:59,279
Boss, are you okay?

622
00:25:59,559 --> 00:26:00,480
What could be wrong with me?

623
00:26:01,200 --> 00:26:03,720
People, you know, shouldn't just pursue material things.

624
00:26:04,039 --> 00:26:05,599
You have to have spiritual pursuits too, right?

625
00:26:06,000 --> 00:26:07,440
I actually only pursue material things right now.

626
00:26:09,279 --> 00:26:09,680
No...

627
00:26:10,240 --> 00:26:12,079
Won't our vegetables go to waste then?

628
00:26:12,400 --> 00:26:12,920
Veggies.

629
00:26:13,559 --> 00:26:13,920
Take them.

630
00:26:15,799 --> 00:26:16,200
Meat.

631
00:26:16,279 --> 00:26:16,640
Take it.

632
00:26:17,000 --> 00:26:17,640
And drinks...

633
00:26:17,640 --> 00:26:17,960
Take them.

634
00:26:18,119 --> 00:26:19,240
Can the wages be raised a bit more?

635
00:26:19,440 --> 00:26:21,039
Aren't you getting a little too comfortable?

636
00:26:22,079 --> 00:26:23,319
Go home and be happy, all of you.

637
00:26:27,799 --> 00:26:29,680
This, this, this... how do I do this?

638
00:26:30,480 --> 00:26:30,839
Cousin.

639
00:26:31,960 --> 00:26:32,519
Let me do it.

640
00:26:33,759 --> 00:26:34,480
As long as I'm here,

641
00:26:35,359 --> 00:26:36,960
I won't let anything stump you.

642
00:26:38,599 --> 00:26:39,240
You do it.

643
00:26:44,440 --> 00:26:45,400
Enter this verification code.

644
00:26:46,519 --> 00:26:48,319
Look, Kong Guifang.

645
00:26:50,000 --> 00:26:51,000
I am simply too handsome.

646
00:26:52,799 --> 00:26:54,319
Didn't you just enter a verification code?

647
00:26:56,279 --> 00:26:56,599
Yes.

648
00:26:58,000 --> 00:26:59,319
But Cousin, do you know?

649
00:27:00,119 --> 00:27:01,440
If you enter the verification code wrong three times,

650
00:27:01,599 --> 00:27:02,640
do you know what the consequences are?

651
00:27:03,240 --> 00:27:03,880
What consequences?

652
00:27:05,000 --> 00:27:06,920
You have to wait another five minutes to log in again.

653
00:27:07,640 --> 00:27:08,079
Whereas I...

654
00:27:08,680 --> 00:27:09,599
only used one try.

655
00:27:23,599 --> 00:27:24,640
Let me see what your major is.

656
00:27:26,759 --> 00:27:27,759
College of Agriculture.

657
00:27:28,960 --> 00:27:29,400
Cousin.

658
00:27:30,119 --> 00:27:31,400
You really aim high.

659
00:27:31,680 --> 00:27:32,720
You have ideals and ambition.

660
00:27:32,799 --> 00:27:34,319
You chose such a great major.

661
00:27:35,799 --> 00:27:37,039
My admiration for you...

662
00:27:37,400 --> 00:27:38,759
can no longer be expressed in words.

663
00:27:39,440 --> 00:27:39,839
I've decided.

664
00:27:40,359 --> 00:27:41,119
I'm going to give you a surprise.

665
00:27:41,519 --> 00:27:42,359
Wait for me. What surprise?

666
00:27:42,720 --> 00:27:43,519
You scared me!

667
00:27:43,759 --> 00:27:44,359
When did you come in?

668
00:27:44,400 --> 00:27:44,960
You're back.

669
00:27:45,480 --> 00:27:45,839
Get away.

670
00:27:46,039 --> 00:27:46,319
What are you doing?

671
00:27:46,400 --> 00:27:46,680
Come here.

672
00:27:46,799 --> 00:27:47,039
No...

673
00:27:47,039 --> 00:27:47,680
I have something to tell you.

674
00:27:47,799 --> 00:27:48,119
What is it?

675
00:27:48,480 --> 00:27:49,000
Don't hit me.

676
00:27:49,000 --> 00:27:49,640
Cousin is right here.

677
00:27:49,640 --> 00:27:50,319
Can't you give me some face?

678
00:27:50,400 --> 00:27:50,839
Don't move.

679
00:27:51,240 --> 00:27:52,119
Keep your hands to yourself.

680
00:27:52,279 --> 00:27:53,000
Out, out, out.

681
00:27:53,119 --> 00:27:54,039
Cousin, I'll be back in a bit.

682
00:27:54,039 --> 00:27:54,519
Out, out, out. Cousin!

683
00:27:54,880 --> 00:27:55,279
Brother.

684
00:27:55,799 --> 00:27:56,839
No, I... I... let me put on my shoes.

685
00:27:57,680 --> 00:27:58,640
Let me go in and stay a bit longer.

686
00:27:58,680 --> 00:27:59,640
You see, since I'm already here...

687
00:27:59,640 --> 00:28:00,519
keep me for a meal.

688
00:28:00,519 --> 00:28:01,119
Stay for dinner, my ass.

689
00:28:01,119 --> 00:28:01,640
Hurry up, go, go, go.

690
00:28:01,640 --> 00:28:01,880
No...

691
00:28:01,880 --> 00:28:03,400
Don't you want to know what I'm actually here for?

692
00:28:04,279 --> 00:28:04,799
What are you here for?

693
00:28:06,559 --> 00:28:07,119
Cousin...

694
00:28:07,519 --> 00:28:08,599
registering the freshman homepage.

695
00:28:08,599 --> 00:28:10,279
Such an important thing, and you're not helping her?

696
00:28:10,960 --> 00:28:12,359
If I weren't there, she wouldn't figure it out.

697
00:28:12,960 --> 00:28:13,839
Cousin needs me right now.

698
00:28:14,039 --> 00:28:14,799
She can't do without me.

699
00:28:14,880 --> 00:28:15,319
Get away, get away.

700
00:28:16,079 --> 00:28:17,119
Step aside. I'm warning you.

701
00:28:17,119 --> 00:28:17,599
Let me tell you.

702
00:28:17,960 --> 00:28:18,759
I'll tell you the truth. What are you doing?

703
00:28:18,759 --> 00:28:19,680
Let me go in and see... I'll... I'll...

704
00:28:19,680 --> 00:28:20,440
I'll tell you the truth.

705
00:28:20,680 --> 00:28:21,440
I'll tell you the truth.

706
00:28:23,200 --> 00:28:23,920
My mom's illness...

707
00:28:35,759 --> 00:28:36,920
Sorry. No... are you okay?

708
00:28:50,599 --> 00:28:51,440
It was just this close.

709
00:28:52,359 --> 00:28:52,920
Just this much.

710
00:28:53,640 --> 00:28:54,640
My butt would've blossomed.

711
00:28:55,839 --> 00:28:56,359
Brother.

712
00:28:57,160 --> 00:28:57,880
You saved my life.

713
00:28:58,559 --> 00:28:58,880
No.

714
00:28:59,480 --> 00:29:00,200
You saved my butt.

715
00:29:01,319 --> 00:29:02,000
To repay you,

716
00:29:02,799 --> 00:29:03,720
alive, I'm your family's ox.

717
00:29:04,119 --> 00:29:04,960
Dead, I'm your family's horse.

718
00:29:05,319 --> 00:29:06,920
Dead or alive, I'll slave away for your family.

719
00:29:09,799 --> 00:29:11,000
If you dare come in, we're done.

720
00:29:13,799 --> 00:29:14,680
Then I'll come back tomorrow.

721
00:29:18,599 --> 00:29:19,400
Was it a coincidence?

722
00:29:20,400 --> 00:29:21,680
My god, Li Wai almost just...

723
00:29:22,200 --> 00:29:23,119
No, just thinking about it hurts.

724
00:29:24,240 --> 00:29:25,200
Could it have something to do with me?

725
00:29:25,960 --> 00:29:26,680
The confidentiality thing.

726
00:29:27,440 --> 00:29:29,480
But shouldn't the punishment only target me?

727
00:29:32,000 --> 00:29:32,559
Where's Li Wai?

728
00:29:33,480 --> 00:29:33,920
He went home.

729
00:29:34,400 --> 00:29:35,119
He went home.

730
00:29:36,000 --> 00:29:37,480
Why didn't he say goodbye before leaving?

731
00:29:38,240 --> 00:29:39,039
Maybe something came up suddenly.

732
00:29:39,200 --> 00:29:40,039
So he didn't... didn't...

733
00:29:40,720 --> 00:29:42,759
Alright, I'll just cook for the two of us then.

734
00:29:42,759 --> 00:29:43,119
Okay.

735
00:29:44,480 --> 00:29:45,559
Brought back from the barbecue shop.

736
00:29:46,400 --> 00:29:47,240
Looks pretty fresh.

737
00:29:47,240 --> 00:29:48,160
Then I'll cook with this.

738
00:29:48,240 --> 00:29:48,599
Is it?

739
00:29:49,720 --> 00:29:51,200
Now that my mom is going to college,

740
00:29:51,200 --> 00:29:52,799
we'll be seeing each other all the time.

741
00:29:52,880 --> 00:29:55,160
Her identity is way too easy to expose.

742
00:29:56,000 --> 00:29:56,319
Mom.

743
00:29:56,880 --> 00:29:57,359
Look here.

744
00:29:58,519 --> 00:30:00,880
You've been admitted to Duxing University now.

745
00:30:00,880 --> 00:30:02,279
Take this and put it in the fridge for me.

746
00:30:02,480 --> 00:30:03,200
From now on, the two of us...

747
00:30:03,200 --> 00:30:04,799
will be living on the same campus.

748
00:30:04,880 --> 00:30:05,920
You have to be careful with your identity.

749
00:30:05,920 --> 00:30:06,559
Don't get exposed.

750
00:30:06,640 --> 00:30:08,000
Just tell people you're my cousin.

751
00:30:08,079 --> 00:30:09,240
Whatever you do, don't say you're my mom.

752
00:30:09,680 --> 00:30:10,960
You've been nagging me about this for a year.

753
00:30:10,960 --> 00:30:12,319
My ears are callused from listening to it.

754
00:30:14,920 --> 00:30:17,119
Then later when I go to register,

755
00:30:17,119 --> 00:30:18,599
if they ask me, what should I say?

756
00:30:18,960 --> 00:30:20,160
Well, if they ask about it...

757
00:30:20,160 --> 00:30:21,079
My... that ID card.

758
00:30:21,079 --> 00:30:22,359
Do I fill in the real one or a fake one?

759
00:30:22,799 --> 00:30:24,200
No, well, you definitely have to fill in the real one.

760
00:30:24,839 --> 00:30:26,000
But about the age...

761
00:30:26,200 --> 00:30:27,519
What if they don't notice the age?

762
00:30:27,519 --> 00:30:28,319
Just... just fudge it.

763
00:30:28,319 --> 00:30:29,759
If it's absolutely unavoidable,

764
00:30:30,319 --> 00:30:32,039
you still have to admit to your age.

765
00:30:32,559 --> 00:30:33,480
As for the rest,

766
00:30:34,039 --> 00:30:36,119
I'll explain the looking young part to the school later.

767
00:30:37,240 --> 00:30:37,559
Okay.

768
00:30:40,839 --> 00:30:41,400
But we... we...

769
00:30:42,359 --> 00:30:43,359
I have to say, Mom.

770
00:30:43,920 --> 00:30:45,839
You're about to be a young, beautiful college student.

771
00:30:45,839 --> 00:30:46,559
But on you...

772
00:30:46,960 --> 00:30:48,279
the middle-aged vibe is still a bit strong.

773
00:30:48,440 --> 00:30:49,880
Like "Community warmth for everyone."

774
00:30:49,880 --> 00:30:50,680
You need to change these clothes.

775
00:30:50,759 --> 00:30:51,680
Let's go buy new clothes in a couple of days.

776
00:30:52,160 --> 00:30:53,359
Don't waste money on me.

777
00:30:53,519 --> 00:30:54,440
This is very durable.

778
00:30:57,640 --> 00:30:59,160
Why buy me so many clothes?

779
00:30:59,160 --> 00:31:00,279
We have all the daily necessities too.

780
00:31:00,920 --> 00:31:02,519
The stuff at home is years old.

781
00:31:02,519 --> 00:31:03,599
You need to buy new ones for school.

782
00:31:03,599 --> 00:31:04,279
That would look so good.

783
00:31:04,279 --> 00:31:05,000
You're just wasting money.

784
00:31:05,000 --> 00:31:05,599
Wash it and it's still usable.

785
00:31:13,559 --> 00:31:14,440
What are you doing? Go in.

786
00:31:15,079 --> 00:31:16,079
Don't block the door, hurry up.

787
00:31:20,920 --> 00:31:22,039
Xu Rui, let's switch seats.

788
00:31:22,519 --> 00:31:23,039
Don't get bumped.

789
00:31:28,359 --> 00:31:29,759
No, buddy, why are you switching seats?

790
00:31:33,200 --> 00:31:34,000
Sorry, sorry.

791
00:31:45,680 --> 00:31:46,640
Where do you think you're going?

792
00:31:47,880 --> 00:31:48,319
Babe.

793
00:31:49,279 --> 00:31:50,000
Surprised?

794
00:31:50,759 --> 00:31:51,240
Shocked?

795
00:31:56,279 --> 00:31:57,160
Let's... let's go outside and talk.

796
00:31:58,599 --> 00:31:59,400
I heard.

797
00:31:59,680 --> 00:32:01,759
You met a pretty new sports student.

798
00:32:02,200 --> 00:32:03,920
Fawning over her everywhere.

799
00:32:04,519 --> 00:32:06,200
I came back as soon as I finished my competition.

800
00:32:07,599 --> 00:32:08,599
I realized.

801
00:32:08,880 --> 00:32:10,759
You really are forever young.

802
00:32:11,519 --> 00:32:12,799
Forever liking sports students.

803
00:32:14,839 --> 00:32:15,559
So consistent.

804
00:32:16,519 --> 00:32:17,079
Little sister.

805
00:32:18,200 --> 00:32:19,359
Did you know he has a girlfriend?

806
00:32:21,759 --> 00:32:22,920
Should I know?

807
00:32:23,599 --> 00:32:24,599
Or should I not know?

808
00:32:25,799 --> 00:32:26,519
Doesn't matter.

809
00:32:27,160 --> 00:32:28,359
You go first or me?

810
00:32:31,160 --> 00:32:31,839
Let's do it together.

811
00:32:34,680 --> 00:32:35,240
Scumbag.

812
00:32:37,519 --> 00:32:38,039
Scumbag.

813
00:32:43,920 --> 00:32:44,680
Sorry, sorry.

814
00:32:45,000 --> 00:32:45,680
Let's take the next one.

815
00:32:46,319 --> 00:32:47,039
Save me.

816
00:32:50,519 --> 00:32:51,039
That's enough.

817
00:32:52,000 --> 00:32:53,640
Stop hitting me! I admitted I was wrong, didn't I?

818
00:32:57,519 --> 00:32:58,279
Not there!

819
00:33:04,599 --> 00:33:05,200
Bro, bro.

820
00:33:05,200 --> 00:33:06,079
Help me, bro!

821
00:33:07,400 --> 00:33:08,519
This is way too melodramatic.

822
00:33:08,759 --> 00:33:09,920
It's like watching a TV drama, Mom.

823
00:33:09,920 --> 00:33:10,920
How can it be like this?

824
00:33:11,119 --> 00:33:12,039
There's something even more melodramatic.

825
00:33:12,720 --> 00:33:13,160
Right.

826
00:33:14,000 --> 00:33:14,480
Right, right, right.

827
00:33:14,839 --> 00:33:16,039
That girl is your high school classmate.

828
00:33:16,039 --> 00:33:16,480
Isn't she?

829
00:33:16,640 --> 00:33:17,519
The one you liked.

830
00:33:17,519 --> 00:33:18,200
You chased after her.

831
00:33:18,480 --> 00:33:20,160
Mom saw that photo at home.

832
00:33:20,960 --> 00:33:21,920
What a coincidence.

833
00:33:21,920 --> 00:33:23,039
How did we all end up here?

834
00:33:23,279 --> 00:33:24,160
That is indeed melodramatic.

835
00:33:24,920 --> 00:33:26,359
The girl is really pretty.

836
00:33:26,799 --> 00:33:28,319
I can understand why she didn't pick you.

837
00:33:28,920 --> 00:33:30,000
But that guy is even worse.

838
00:33:30,319 --> 00:33:31,319
She'd be better off with my son.

839
00:33:34,079 --> 00:33:35,599
Son, Mom didn't mean that.

840
00:33:37,039 --> 00:33:37,799
This... this mouth.

841
00:34:02,200 --> 00:34:03,000
You want a beating too?

842
00:34:05,599 --> 00:34:06,000
No.

843
00:34:07,079 --> 00:34:07,559
Xu Rui.

844
00:34:08,760 --> 00:34:09,840
I want to explain to you.

845
00:34:10,400 --> 00:34:11,320
Back then, my mom was critically ill.

846
00:34:11,679 --> 00:34:12,920
My family had no money left.

847
00:34:13,159 --> 00:34:14,280
I felt I wasn't good enough for you.

848
00:34:14,559 --> 00:34:15,840
I thought breaking up was for your own good.

849
00:34:16,400 --> 00:34:18,079
Until today, seeing you with someone else...

850
00:34:18,719 --> 00:34:20,199
...I realized I can't live without you.

851
00:34:20,440 --> 00:34:21,119
Kong Xiaocan.

852
